Package com.github.jonathanxd.iutils.list

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PredicateList<E>
    A predicate list, the PredicateList.isAcceptable(Object) method is called before adding the element, if it returns false, this list calls PredicateList.onReject(Object) and does not add the element.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractPredicateList<E>
    Abstract implementation of PredicateList.
    AbstractPredicateWrappedList<E>
    Abstract implementation of a PredicateList backed by a List.
    DynamicSizedJavaList<E>
    A Dynamic size limited implementation of List.
    ListSet<E> Deprecated
    PredicateArrayList<E> Deprecated
    Use PredicateWrappedList.
    PredicateWrappedFailingList<E>
    A PredicateList backed by a List.
    PredicateWrappedList<E>
    A PredicateList backed by a List.
    PredicateWrappedListIterator<E>  
    SizedJavaList<E>
    A size limited implementation of List.
    StaticList<T> Deprecated
    StaticListSet<T> Deprecated
    UniqueList<E>
    An AbstractPredicateWrappedList that does not allow duplicated elements and does not throw exceptions when trying to add duplicated elements.
